{
  "text": "Viral infection may also trigger sudden SNHL combined with BPPV, inflaming and damaging the labyrinth, accompanied by vestibulopathy and Bell's palsy [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . Karlberg et al. [CITATION_3] considered that viral infection of the labyrinth might trigger BPPV.",
